body:
debugging a performance regression in my code, found it was introduced between `nightly-2018-11-03` and `nightly-2018-11-04` - https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/compare/8b096314a...04fdb44f5

the best minimum example i could come up with:

```rust
    #[bench]
    fn bench_something(b: &mut Bencher) {
        b.iter(|| {
            (0..1000)
                .for_each(|a| {
                    let mut vec = Vec::with_capacity(10);
                    vec.push(0);
                    vec.push(0);
                    vec.push(0);
                    vec.push(0);
                    vec.push(0);
                    vec.push(0);
                    vec.push(0);
                    vec.push(0);
                    vec.push(0);
                    vec.push(0);
                })
        });
    }
```

test between the two versions:
```
